Author: externalmusings
Text: THIS just found out last night that my roommate and her boyfriend ate 6 (SIX!) of my eggs over the weekend which are one of my few safe foods/protein sources let alone one of the few foods I actually keep around :( Didn't confront her about it in fear of crying and looking irrational but FUCK dude that shit hurted   I hope you acquire another sweet potato soon so you can have the physical energy to FIGHT your family<3
